SONIX TECH said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 21.87% to NT$324,748,000 from NT$415,656,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            324,748          415,656    
YOY%             -21.87%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,054,975        1,194,249   
YOY%             -11.66% 
